<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="563" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Faldermann" baseAuthorityYear="1836" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion lucidum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Faldermann, 1836 was retained, after a study of the type specimen by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="41 - 50" refId="B40" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1910. Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion -Arten. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung 29: 41 - 50, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" title="Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion - Arten." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" volume="29" year="1910">Netolitzky (1910)</bibRefCitation>
as being very close to 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. dalmatinum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dalmatinum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dalmatinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Dejean, 1831. Later 
<bibRefCitation author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B42" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1914b. Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10(7/8): 164-176." title="Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10 (7 / 8): 164 - 176." year="1914 b">Netolitzky (1914b)</bibRefCitation>
synonymized 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Faldermann" baseAuthorityYear="1836" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion lucidum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1831" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion dalmatinum" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dalmatinum">Bembidion dalmatinum</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Menetries" authorityYear="1832" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion fraxator" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fraxator">Bembidion fraxator</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
, 1832 (currently 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Menetries" authorityYear="1832" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Bembidion fraxator" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fraxator">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">Bembidion fraxator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is considered a valid species). 
<bibRefCitation author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Apollo Books, Stenstrup" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B28" refString="Marggi, W, Huber, C, Mueller-Motzfeld, G, Hartmann, M, 2003. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242-273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Apollo Books, Stenstrup" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 242 - 273. In: Loebl I, Smetana A (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. 1). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2003">Marggi et al. (2003</bibRefCitation>
: 271) listed 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. lucidum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. dimidiatum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dimidiatum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dimidiatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
, 1832 which was moved to &quot;incertae sedis&quot;; while the moving of 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. dimidiatum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dimidiatum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dimidiatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was mentioned (p. 21) nothing was stated about 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. lucidum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. This situation remains also in 
<bibRefCitation author="Marggi, W" journalOrPublisher="Brill, Leiden" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B29" refString="Marggi, W, Toledano, L, Neri, P, 2017. Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294-342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga. Brill, Leiden" title="Carabidae: Bembidiini: Bembidiina: 294 - 342. In: Loebl I, Loebl D (Eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera (Vol. I). Archostemata - Myxophaga - Adephaga." year="2017">Marggi et al. (2017)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="563">
After having carefully analyzed the literature regarding these taxa (e.g., 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.51784" author="Menetries, E" journalOrPublisher="Academie Imperiale des Sciences, St. Petersbourg" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B30" refString="Menetries, E, 1832. Catalogue raisonne des objets de zoologie recueillis dans un voyage au Caucase et jusqu'aux frontieres actuelles de la Perse. Academie Imperiale des Sciences, St. Petersbourg, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.51784" title="Catalogue raisonne des objets de zoologie recueillis dans un voyage au Caucase et jusqu'aux frontieres actuelles de la Perse." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.51784" year="1832">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
1832
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Faldermann, F" journalOrPublisher="Nouveaux Memoires de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes de Moscau" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="1 - 310" refId="B10" refString="Faldermann, F, 1836. Coleoptera Persico Armenica. I. Pentamera (citata anche come: &quot;Fauna Entomologica Tanscaucasica. I&quot;). Nouveaux Memoires de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes de Moscau 4 (1836): 1 - 310" title="Coleoptera Persico Armenica. I. Pentamera (citata anche come: &quot; Fauna Entomologica Tanscaucasica. I &quot;)." volume="4" year="1836">Faldermann 1836</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Schaum, H" journalOrPublisher="Berliner Entomologische Zeitschrift" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="199 - 215" refId="B49" refString="Schaum, H, 1861. Synonymische Bemerkungen. II. Berliner Entomologische Zeitschrift 5: 199 - 215" title="Synonymische Bemerkungen. II." volume="5" year="1861">Schaum 1861</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="41 - 50" refId="B40" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1910. Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion -Arten. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung 29: 41 - 50, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" title="Ueber einige wenig bekannte Bembidion - Arten." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.23333" volume="29" year="1910">Netolitzky 1910</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Netolitzky, F" journalOrPublisher="Wiener Entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" refId="B42" refString="Netolitzky, F, 1914b. Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10(7/8): 164-176." title="Die Bembidiini in Winklers Catalogus. Entomologische Blatter 10 (7 / 8): 164 - 176." year="1914 b">1914b</bibRefCitation>
; Kryzhanovskij et al. 1995; 
<bibRefCitation author="Belousov, IA" journalOrPublisher="Stuttgarter Beitraege zur Naturkunde, (A, Biologie)" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" pagination="1 - 40" refId="B4" refString="Belousov, IA, Sokolov, IM, 1996. Review of the Caucasian Species of the subgenus Peryphanes Jeannel (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Bembidion). Stuttgarter Beitraege zur Naturkunde, (A, Biologie) 40 (549): 1 - 40" title="Review of the Caucasian Species of the subgenus Peryphanes Jeannel (Coleoptera: Carabidae: Bembidion)." volume="40" year="1996">Belousov and Sokolov 1996</bibRefCitation>
), we confirm that 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. lucidum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="lucidum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. lucidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Faldermann is a synonym of 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. fraxator" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="fraxator">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. fraxator</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
and not of 
<taxonomicName genus="B." lsidName="B. dimidiatum" pageId="0" pageNumber="563" rank="species" species="dimidiatum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="563">B. dimidiatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Ménétriés">Menetries</normalizedToken>
, which, moreover, belongs to another subgenus (see above).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
